data.description: Large custom home in a great neighborhood. It has 5 bedrooms and 4 baths. It includes a 1400 sq ft finished basement that is not included in the square footage. The home has a large living room, dining room and hobby room. Plus, In-Law quarters.  A balcony provides a quiet sitting area for outside living. There is a large, covered patio off the kitchen. The yard is spacious and landscaped. with storage shed. House is one of a kind in the area.
